    "We also used separate calls for each category (EBM-PICO) and entity mention pair (ChemProt and DDI) to ensure the consistency of prompts with long-text examples.",
    "The precise prompt texts used in experiments are provided in Appendix A.",
    "For each LLM and each dataset, six experiments were run varying the length of the prompt, number of examples, and the example selection strategy.",
    "The same prompts were used to interact with all LLMs; full prompts are available in Appendix A.",
    "An overview of the evaluation strategy is provided in Figure 1."
